Your organization manages AWS network security rules through a centralized CSV file. You have been tasked with automating the creation of VPC Security Group rules, 
  generating structured outputs from CSV data, and fetching existing subnet information using data sources.

The following files are provided:

challenge-2/
├── main.tf
├── outputs.tf
├── sg.csv              ← Security group rules definition file
├── instances.csv       ← Instance details CSV file
└── variables.tf

